// HistoryModal
// Full-screen modal showing a diff between a historical document version and
// the current version. Opened from the document editor's history toolbar.

FUNCTION formatRelativeTime(ts) -> string
  Just now (<5s), Xs ago (<60s), Xm ago (<1h), Xh ago (<24h),
  Yesterday, Xd ago, or locale date string.

---

FUNCTION HistoryModal(historicalContent, currentContent, version, onClose, onRevert) -> JSX  EXPORT
  CALLS: DiffView (DiffView)
  Renders a backdrop + centered modal.
  Backdrop click closes. Escape closes. Body scroll prevented while open.
  Shows formatted relative timestamp as title.
  Shows DiffView between historicalContent and currentContent.
  Revert button calls onRevert(historicalContent) and closes.

---

FUNCTION handleBackdropClick(e) -> void
  Calls onClose only if the click was on the backdrop itself (not the modal).
